title: Germany's Merkel backs WHO as calls for more coronavirus cooperation
meta_description: BERLIN - German Chancellor Angela Merkel stressed the need for more global cooperation to tackle the coronavirus pandemic on Thursday and voiced support for the World Health Organisation after the United States cut its funding.
